Paper: hep-th/0209031

Date: 2002-09-04

Title: The WZW model on Random Regge Triangulations

Authors: G. Arcioni, M. Carfora, C. Dappiaggi, A. Marzuoli

Comments: 16 pages, uses "xy.tex" package

By exploiting the correspondence between Random Regge triangulations (i.e.,Regge triangulations with variable connectivity) and punctured Riemannsurfaces, we are able to characterize the SU(2) Wess-Zumino-Witten model on atriangulated surface of genus g.